---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Events - Phoebe Dawson Foundation" currentPath="/events">
    <!-- ============ PAGE HERO ============ -->
    <section class="page-hero">
        <img src="/assets/cole-classic-1.jpg" alt="Events">
        <div class="page-hero-overlay">
            <h1>Events & Fundraising</h1>
            <p class="page-hero-subtitle">Join Team WWPD</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ INTRO SECTION ============ -->
    <section class="intro-section">
        <div class="intro-content">
            <h2>Join the Journey</h2>
            <p>In 2026, we aim to expand our impact through two signature annual events. We invite you to join us‚Äîwhether by attending our events, purchasing our commemorative swimwear, or launching your own fundraising challenges.</p>
            <p>Together, we can ensure that Phoebe's knack for brightening lives continues to make the world a better place for children and families in need.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ EVENTS GRID ============ -->
    <section class="events-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">2026 Events</h2>
        <div class="events-grid">
            <div class="event-card">
                <img src="/assets/sun-run-2025-2.jpg" alt="Dee Why to Manly Sun Run">
                <div class="event-card-content">
                    <span class="event-date">Saturday 31st January 2026</span>
                    <h3>Sun Run</h3>
                    <p>The 10km Dee Why to Manly Sun Run kicks off our signature weekend of WWPD events. Join Team WWPD as we continue our tradition of swimming and running to exceed our previous fundraising milestones.</p>
                    <a href="https://raceroster.com/events/2026/110486/sun-run-2026" target="_blank" class="event-btn">Enter Now</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="event-card">
                <img src="/assets/cole-classic-1.jpg" alt="Cole Classic Ocean Swim">
                <div class="event-card-content">
                    <span class="event-date">Sunday 1st February 2026</span>
                    <h3>Cole Classic</h3>
                    <p>The world's biggest ocean swim! Team WWPD will be swimming in custom yellow and white swimmers. Following the event, join us for a BBQ celebration at Little Manly‚Äîthe beautiful location where Phoebe and Tim were married.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="event-btn secondary">Entries Closed</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="event-card">
                <img src="/assets/Art_Gallery_of_New_South_Wales,_2022,_09.jpg" alt="Phoebe Dawson Gala">
                <div class="event-card-content">
                    <span class="event-date">Saturday 13th June 2026</span>
                    <h3>Phoebe Dawson Gala</h3>
                    <p>A celebration held to coincide with Phoebe's birthday, bringing together her large circle of family and friends to fundraise for critical health services. Black tie at the Art Gallery of NSW.</p>
                    <a href="#" class="event-btn secondary">Coming Soon</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ GET INVOLVED ============ -->
    <section class="get-involved-section">
        <h2 class="section-title">Ways to Get Involved</h2>
        <div class="involve-grid">
            <div class="involve-card">
                <div class="involve-icon">üèä</div>
                <h3>Join an Event</h3>
                <p>Swim, run, or attend the gala‚Äîbe part of the WWPD team and help us raise funds for causes close to Phoebe's heart.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="involve-card">
                <div class="involve-icon">üíõ</div>
                <h3>Donate</h3>
                <p>Support our fundraising efforts directly. Every contribution helps us support Bear Cottage, Royal Far West, and Angel Flight.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="involve-card">
                <div class="involve-icon">üëô</div>
                <h3>Buy Swimwear</h3>
                <p>Purchase our commemorative yellow and white WWPD swimmers and show your support at the beach.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="involve-card">
                <div class="involve-icon">üéØ</div>
                <h3>Start a Challenge</h3>
                <p>Launch your own fundraising challenge and rally your community to support the Foundation.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="involve-cta">
            <a href="https://phoebe-dawson-foundation.grassrootz.com/" target="_blank" class="donate-btn">Donate Now</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ PAST EVENTS ============ -->
    <section class="past-events">
        <div class="past-events-content">
            <div class="past-events-text">
                <h2>Past Events</h2>
                <p>In early February 2025, 29 intrepid swimmers participated in the Cole Classic "the world's biggest ocean swim" under the WWPD (What Would Phoebe Do) banner. All participants wore custom yellow and white swimmers with WWPD branding.</p>
                <p>The previous day, 10 participants took part in the 10km Dee Why to Manly Sun Run. These events brought together participants of all ages and helped build awareness of the foundation's mission to support causes close to Phoebe's heart.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="past-events-image">
                <img src="/assets/group.jpg" alt="Team WWPD">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============ FULL BANNER ============ -->
    <section class="full-banner">
        <img src="/assets/LittleManly.jpg" alt="Little Manly">
        <div class="full-banner-overlay">
            <h2>"Join Team WWPD and make a difference in our community"</h2>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>

